reviewText: Great collection of movies for value.
nice to have these

These are a few of my daughter's favorite movies, and mine, if the truth were to be told.  I was pleased to get them all in a set and for a good price.  There were no scratches or problems of any sort, and she's happy as a clam (are clams really happy?) with her gift.  I'm a happy clam too.
Love all these movies. Perfect bundle for fairytales.

Great value. 4 great movies in a package and all are very good and entertaining to watch.
Prompt, product as described. Nice to have these movies in a compact bundle.
I really like that a few of my favorite Romance movies are together at a great price.  It was worth the purchase.
as expected
Getting 4 for the price of one... great deal... works great... great service and delivery...
Great Quality

Four great movies. I was really just looking to replace my VHS copies of Princess Bride and Ever After, but it was cheaper to buy this than single DVDs of those two movies. Mirror Mirror was a bonus, and I already have T&I on another disc set. But a great set of movies, for sure!
Nice collection.
Loved all four  of  the  movies

I order many movies on DVD and am especially fond of older movies and classics. When I saw this collection I couldn't wait. But I was very disappointed in the condition of the DVD The Princess Bride. It has irreparable damage and is unwatchable. The others are fine (as far as I can tell). I will have to think twice before ordering again.

4 excellent family friendly movies in one box collection. My kids loved them.

Ordered this for The Princess Bride for my daughter (we already had Mirror, Mirror).  She enjoyed the movie very much and thought it was exciting and romantic.  Haven't watched Tristan and Isolde  yet and it's been awhile since we saw Ever After which I remember as a Cinderella story,  but the primary reason for getting this was The Princess Bride.
